Installation (pull-only repo)

    git clone git://github.com/jaredcobb/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Installation (ssh)

    git clone git@github.com:jaredcobb/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Symlinks

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Initialize other sandboxes

	Since I'm using submodules, here's how you get the plugins

	cd ~/.vim
	git submodule init
	git submodule update

Pull submodules that have updates

	git submodule foreach git pull
